preference.name: CATIA_compare_uid_reference_top_level_on_merge
preference.preference_description: When the top level loaded in CATIA has not the same file name as the top level of the selected document in Teamcenter but they have the same item revision UID, set to true to perform a Load Merge operation; otherwise set to false to perform a Load Merge under reference product operation.
